dialogue: This staff looks good. (Pick the staff)
This sword looks sharp. (Pick the longsword)
This bow looks brand new. (Pick the bow)
The one down the road. (Go by the path further down the road)
I'll take the one on the left. (Slide down the slope on the left)
No thanks. I'll be on my way.
Alright. I'll you up on that offer.
